This Perl module provides an OOP interface to the http://www.disqus.com/ API.

Documentation
  You can find the documentation for this module in a couple of files:

    * Disqus.pod -- This file describes the data model, and the API functions in one place.

    * INSTALL -- This file provides the installation instructions.

    * Each module, and sub-module's perldoc page describes the corresponding piece.

      * perldoc Net::Disqus

      * perldoc Net::Disqus::Author

      * perldoc Net::Disqus::Post

      * perldoc Net::Disqus::Thread

      * perldoc Net::Disqus::Forum

  You can find more information from these sources:

    * The Disqus web page -- <http://www.disqus.com/>

    * The Disqus main API documentation -- <http://wiki.disqus.net/API>

    * This module's CPAN page -- <http://search.cpan.org/search?query=Net%3A%3ADisqus&mode=all>

    * This module's github wiki -- <http://wiki.github.com/goozbach/perl-Net-Disqus>

    * This module's github issue tracker -- <http://github.com/goozbach/perl-Net-Disqus/issues>

